snippet.textDisplay:
This song is truly an emotion in itself. Every single word, every line, takes me back to those days and makes me feel so numb, yet so alive at the same time. It’s incredible how a man can write such profound lyrics that resonate so deeply with our experiences. It’s a masterpiece that captures the essence of nostalgia, reminding us of moments we hold dear.

Listening to it feels like a journey through time, where each note pulls at my heartstrings and evokes memories I thought I had forgotten. It’s as if the artist reached into our souls and expressed what we couldn’t put into words. The way the lyrics paint vivid pictures of love, loss, and longing is nothing short of magical. 

In a world that often feels chaotic and overwhelming, this song serves as a refuge, a reminder of the beauty in simplicity and the power of connection. It makes me reflect on the moments that shaped me, the laughter shared, and the tears shed. It’s a reminder that even in our busiest times, we can find solace in music that speaks to our hearts. This song is more than just lyrics,it’s a feeling, a memory, and a reminder that we’re all in this together.

snippet.textDisplay:
Since everyone is telling their stories ..I'll add mine too ...(i got to know about this song from him)

So I'm 17 years ols... When I Passed my class 10th board.. I took Admission in a college .. I met a guy there.. Actually he was my brother's roommate (my brother and I are same year old , he's my uncle's son) . So we talked through my brother sometimes .. then my brother changed room and we had no connection then ..I didn't feel anything back then ..but after that the guy and me took the same tuition ..so we were talking again whenever we meet but we never messaged each other.. one day in summer vacation 15 th of july .. he msged me... (I wish I didn't reply him that day) .. so somehow talking like this we became close day by day ..then we fell in love.. he always used to ask me "I wanna touch the sky , will you go with me?" At first I said as a friend.. but slowly I replied yes I'll go with you .. I fell for him.. we started iur relationship.. I thought he'd be my fast and last.. but then his ex showed up .. messed with him .. she even blamed me.. idk what happened after that.. few days later he said he got his feelings back for her.. he said she is his first luv he can't forget her .. that is how it ended.. 

IDK why am I still holding onto us ?? Why do I still love him? Idk anything.. I see him everyday.. not only him I see them always together in college.. it's actually too hard to heal a heart whilr being a good student.. I was a topper in school .. as well as  I'm the roll no 1 in the class .. so  it's too hard to maintain everything... I feel so broken.. my academic results have got low.. 

Idk what should I do.. how do I cope with the pain .. how do I accept everything... idk .. 
I just find myself keep coming back to this song again and again🌹❤


So hey my dear strangers ! Help me find a way to be happy and to be the old me!
